
Steps of ELF Calculation and analysis

Afetr optimization of the system do an SCF calculation with LELF = .TRUE. 
Plot the ELFCAR in vesta to see the electron localization around each element and bond
Red --- indicates high electron density while Blue ---- indicates low electron density

